# {{.Name}}

MCP server generated by [mint](https://github.com/sirerun/mint) from an OpenAPI specification.

## Usage

### Build

```bash
go mod tidy
go build -o {{.Name}} .
```

### Run with stdio transport

```bash
./{{.Name}} --transport stdio
```

### Run with SSE transport

```bash
./{{.Name}} --transport sse --port 8080
```

### Configure in Claude Desktop

Add to your `claude_desktop_config.json`:

```json
{
  "mcpServers": {
    "{{.Name}}": {
      "command": "/path/to/{{.Name}}",
      "args": ["--transport", "stdio"]
    }
  }
}
```

## CLI Mode

List all available tools:

```bash
./{{.Name}} tools
```

Call a tool with arguments:

```bash
./{{.Name}} call <tool_name> key=value ...
```

Call with compact JSON output:

```bash
./{{.Name}} call <tool_name> --raw key=value ...
```

